# Approach : Bit manipulation
# Difficulty : Easy
# Time Complexity : O(n)
# Space Complexity : O(1)

```python 
class Solution(object):
    def singleNumber(self, nums):
        res=0
        for i in nums:
            res=res^i               #-->XOR (Which Cancels the same element)  
        return res                  # -->Returns the unique element



Input :
nums =[2,2,1]
Output :
1
